sequenceDiagram
    participant Player
    participant PackScreen
    participant IdentificationService
    participant StatRoller
    participant WriteQueue
    participant Supabase
    participant ObservabilityService

    Player->>PackScreen: Long-press unidentified + enriched card
    PackScreen->>PackScreen: Start hold timer, show charge animation (particles converge)

    Note over PackScreen: At 1200ms threshold
    PackScreen->>IdentificationService: Trigger identification

    IdentificationService->>StatRoller: Roll stats for instanceUUID
    StatRoller->>StatRoller: SHA-256(instanceUUID) to seed
    StatRoller->>StatRoller: Distribute brawn/wit/speed (sum=90, +/-30% from species baseline)
    StatRoller->>StatRoller: Determine size from species size band, weight from size range
    StatRoller->>StatRoller: Roll affixes based on rarity (CR=2, EN=1-2, VU=0-1, NT/LC=0)
    StatRoller-->>IdentificationService: Rolled stats, size, weight, prefix, suffix

    IdentificationService->>PackScreen: Reveal card data
    PackScreen->>PackScreen: Particle burst, full TCG card revealed with stats, art, name, affixes

    IdentificationService->>IdentificationService: Optimistic update: local item identified=true with rolled stats

    IdentificationService->>WriteQueue: Enqueue {action: identify, item_id, brawn, wit, speed, size, weight, prefix, suffix}
    WriteQueue->>Supabase: UPDATE v3_items SET identified=true, brawn=X, ...<br/>WHERE id=Y AND identified=false (idempotent guard)

    alt Success
        Supabase-->>WriteQueue: Success
        WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Mark CONFIRMED
        WriteQueue->>ObservabilityService: Log identify.completed
    else Write fails
        Supabase-->>WriteQueue: Error
        WriteQueue->>WriteQueue: Retry with backoff
        Note over WriteQueue: Stats are deterministic,<br/>so re-roll produces same result
    end
